<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Founders in Austin</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 64px 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-top: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .muted {
      color: #666;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: 1px solid #111;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 96px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

    <h1>Founders in Austin</h1>
    <p>One person. One story. One room.</p>
    <p class="muted">Invite only.</p>

    <a href="#invite" class="button">Request an Invite</a>

    <h2>What This Is</h2>
    <p>
      This is a small, private gathering for people building real things in Austin.
    </p>
    <p>
      Each event features one founder, early employee, or solo hacker working on something genuinely interesting.
    </p>
    <p>
      No panels. No pitching. No bullshit.
    </p>

    <h2>Next Event</h2>
    <p>
      Speaker announced privately<br />
      Austin, Texas<br />
      Limited seats
    </p>

    <h2>Who Attends</h2>
    <p>
      Founders<br />
      Early startup employees<br />
      Engineers and operators<br />
      Builders who prefer listening over talking
    </p>

    <h2 id="invite">Request an Invite</h2>
    <p>
      Attendance is invite only.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you are building something interesting in Austin, request access below.
    </p>

    <a href="mailto:hello@yourdomain.com" class="button">Request Access</a>
